{"tid":87671,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"團年飯叫工人煮十二個餸","createTime":"2017-01-20T04:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T09:08:06.000Z","uid":5077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a57292a299a94a7c791c30e63bec1c3caaae5a86","tid":87671,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:31:13.000Z","msg":"有時好睇唔過眼家姐咁mean,<br />\n個個兄弟姊妹都已經成家立室,<br />\n今年家姐話既然俾錢請左個工人,做咩唔叫佢煮,洗乜晒錢去酒樓食<br />\n佢仲好興奮咁諗左好多菜式話想食,想叫工人煮成12個餸,又花膠、又海參、又鮑魚咁<br />\n我地個個兄弟姊妹都話個工人平時煮野都麻麻地,仲叫佢一日煮成12個餸邊有可能<br />\n而且呢d菜式又唔係易整,到時整到唔三唔四咪仲衰<br />\n但我家姐勁堅持,又搵晒食譜同youtube片話俾工人學<br />\n我心諗,度縮就度縮啦,去酒樓夾餐飯咪千幾蚊,係到搞咁多野<br />\n<br />\n佢日日係屋企個whatsapp group send野出黎都無人想理佢"},{"pid":"2353d3dd35ef685b1ea0c0ab0438b602f3a06d5a","tid":87671,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b271745838558a6a685e3ffcf4ccb3f988f94c72","tid":87671,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:34:23.000Z","msg":"鳩UP大師"},{"pid":"726bfcbb46d67bb70874b5c72706589ec66749df","tid":87671,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳩UP大師</blockquote>"},{"pid":"10aa781783dc0091da8197c1de4a7d07249899c9","tid":87671,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:48:57.000Z","msg":"一班人係自己地方可以圍威喂呀麻"},{"pid":"be21894a329265fa389a42d5177c281ff3799cf8","tid":87671,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:08:06.000Z","msg":"叫佢自己煮"}]}